          "experiment_extension_reason": "I'd like to request permission to extend an OT for this API. The experiment has been running for Android only so far, but in the meanwhile:\n1- There has been progress on the spec https://wicg.github.io/digital-credentials/ and it is expected to graduate to the FedID WG soon.\n2- We have added Desktop cross-device support.\n\nTherefore, we are requesting the extension.\n",
