          "ot_use_counter_bucket_number": null,
          "ot_webfeature_use_counter": null,
          "extensions": [],
          "experiment_extension_reason": "- W3C team report on Digital Credentials formal objection is now published with, as expected, a recommendation to overrule the objection: https://www.w3.org/2024/10/team-report-fedid-wg-fo.html\n\n- We have made progress with updating the spec and updated the implementation to match the latest spec (changing the request and response format, and support multiple requests) and we would like to test such implementation. \n\n- Google Birthday Correct Flow implementation is also being updated to support both legacy and modern format.\n\n- We have delayed announcing the cross-device OT because of issue with 3rd party camera apps, we have reached out to other OEMs to fix it.",
